Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:49.90,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}奇跡は誰が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:52.59,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}起こすかなんて
