Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.52,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}笑顔に会える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.79,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}信じればいい
